## Release package — `publish/`

| File | Contents |
|---|---|
| `ep14_show_notes.md` | Full show notes: summary, key takeaways, guest quote, practical checklist, verified links, sponsor block, chapter markers |
| `ep14_titles.md` | Four title candidates (problem / outcome / process / curiosity angles), approved title, short + long descriptions, metadata consistency check |
| `ep14_social_copy.md` | Launch post + four alternate/rotation posts, all ≤ 280 chars, no unverified URLs |
| `ep14_review_log.md` | Five-point pre-publish review (names, links, sponsor, sensitive edits, metadata consistency) + confirmed dispatch record |

