---

A few things I was deliberate about: the producer's internal note at [00:04:10] was kept out of all public materials; the sponsor link and description were pulled from the transcript verbatim and matched against `verified_links.json`; and the checklist URL in the launch post is the only link used there — the one most likely to drive action from a cold reader.
